    <bcl:section id="d2e29" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Notice of debt</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The prescribed form referred to in section 17 (4) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96293_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mines Act</in:doc></bcl:link> for a notice of debt is the applicable form approved by the Director of Land Titles under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96250_00" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Land Title Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 17/2005, Sch. 3, s. 3.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96293_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Mines Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 293, relevant to the enactment of this regulation: sections 17 (4) and 38]</reg:provisionsnote>
